channel.title: Best of Auxy 2021 (in my opinion)
channel.description:
Hello Auxy Disco! Over this year I have attempted to put together (in my humble opinion) the best auxy tracks of 2021 into a playlist. Feel free to repost and let me know if you think there are any great tracks that I should add to it.
https://soundcloud.com/tolberto_auxy/sets/auxy-2021
